These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, skateboard, snowmobile, trike
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade, sprite, mirinda, coffee
5 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, horse, rabbit, snake
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, june, november, may, december
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is the person driving the trike##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
10. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
11. the owner of the hamster is the person who's birthday is in february##1
12. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Transport         | motorbike  | bus    | snowmobile | skateboard    | trike  |
| Beverage   | lemonade  | soy-milk | sprite | mirinda | coffee  |
| Pet           | frog     | snake     | rabbit  | hamster   | horse    |
| Birthday         | november | may    | june | february  | december |

