.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, cucumber, kiwi, lettuce, watermelon
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, car, quad-bike, taxi, airplane
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: disco, r&b, indie, blues, classical
5 different games are played: billiard, go, chess, poker, canasta
 1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 2. the person playing chess is the fan of r&b##1
 3. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 4. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the fan of indie##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is the fan of indie##1
 9. the person playing poker is the person eating kiwi##1
10. the person eating cucumber is in the middle##1
11. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person playing chess##1
12. the person eating kiwi is the person driving the car##1
13. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Food          | kiwi        | watermelon | cucumber     | lettuce      | artichoke  |
| Transport           | car   | quad-bike | airplane    | taxi | boat |
| Music-Genre   | indie | blues     | classical | disco    | r&b  |
| Game   | poker     | go | billiard    | canasta      | chess    |

