.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, sprite, tea, water
5 different pets are kept: goldfish, turtle, goat, fish, mouse
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, zinnia, lily, azalea, iris
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: satire, adventure, family, mystery, sports
 1. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 3. the person who growsbellflower is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 5. the person who growslily is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1
 7. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 8. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
11. the person who growslily is the owner of the goldfish##1
12. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
13. the person drinking tea is the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | tea          | sprite  | milk       | fanta     | water      |
| Pet         | turtle | mouse | fish  | goat   | goldfish    |
| Flower   | zinnia        | iris | bellflower | azalea    | lily   |
| Movie-Genre     | satire   | family | sports      | adventure | mystery |

