.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, october, may, january, june
5 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster, bird, cat, frog
House: cape-cod, futuristic, modern, cottage, tower
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, taxi, van
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the futuristic house is the owner of the hamster##1
 4. the cape-cod house is the owner of the goldfish##1
 5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the cottage house##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 8. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
 9. the cottage house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is the modern house##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
12. the person driving the bike is on the left of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Birthday          | january        | december       | may | october   | june  |
| Pet   | frog | bird | hamster | goldfish   | cat |
| House   | cottage         | tower     | futuristic | cape-cod | modern     |
| Transport     | bike        | car        | van    | taxi    | ship      |

