 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the alhambra-smoker##1
 3. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 6. the baccarat-smoker is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person driving the ship is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the car is in the middle##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
12. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
