 3. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the electrician##1
 5. the person eating radish is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
 7. the person watching scientific movies is the person eating watermelon##1
 8. the person eating radish is the wooden house##1
 9. the firefighter is on the far left##1
10. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
11. the police-officer is in the middle##1
12. the person eating radish is the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |     3      |     4     |       5       |
