10. the turkish is in the middle##1
11. the person playing chess is on the left of the turkish##1
12. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
13. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
14. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
