 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the person who's sport is ivory-polo is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 6. the person driving the airplane is the person who's sport is golf##1
 7. the person who likes ivory is the person who's sport is golf##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who likes lavender##1
11. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's sport is handball##1
12. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
13. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
