 3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the american##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the french##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the person who's sport is rugby is the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the american is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person driving the train##1
10. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
12. the person who's sport is volleyball is the canadian##1
13. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Transport      | trike      | skateboard       | car         | train  | helicopter |
| Sport   | volleyball  | surfing | rugby | tennis  | sailing  |
| Nationality   | canadian    | french    | american        | indonesian | pakistani     |
| Pet           | hedgehog | mouse      | ferret       | pony   | rabbit   |

