The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, may, march, january, february
The people have 5 different hobbies: rock-climbing, video-games, camping, filmmaking, photography
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 3. the fan of trance is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who likes apricot##1
 6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 7. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 8. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
10. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
11. the fan of blues is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
12. the fan of rock is the person who likes black##1
13. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who likes blue##1

