.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda, sprite
There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, emerald, ivory, light-blue, green
There 5 different types of food: watermelon, onion, cabbage, pepper, nectarine
City: liverpool, nizza, hannover, prague, new-york
 1. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 2. the person who likes light-blue is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 4. the person who likes blue is the person eating nectarine##1
 5. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1
 6. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person who likes ivory is the person eating onion##1
 8. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
11. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1
12. the person who likes green is in the middle##1
13. the person eating watermelon is the person drinking mirinda##1
14. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda   | milk    | cola       | sprite |
| Color   | ivory           | emerald   | green   | light-blue       | blue  |
| Food   | onion       | watermelon | cabbage | pepper     | nectarine   |
| City     | hannover    | nizza   | prague   | liverpool | new-york   |

 